&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;C608E0CA50E16897B1BB7FCD492703E7D20308C8&#x2F;52545.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Carrion Devourer&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;07EA03060306A6D95752C70CA7D8931420069B0D&#x2F;52604.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Black Widow Spider&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;31914,12537,12498,12496,63163&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;30,33,72&#x27; data-armory-30-traits=&#x27;1069,1846,1064&#x27; data-armory-33-traits=&#x27;1099,1101,1701&#x27; data-armory-72-traits=&#x27;2301,2278,2271&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;general-rotation&quot;&gt;General Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The entirety of quickness Untamed rotation can be summarised into two steps.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opener (optional)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickness Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repeat&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;precast&quot;&gt;Precast&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12537&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Sharpening Stone&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;opener&quot;&gt;Opener&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The opener can give a very good burst, especially when the boss has different phases.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63344&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Pet&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All your Utility Skills (7&#x2F;8&#x2F;9)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 pet skills (can be cast simultaneously)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63209&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Venomous Outburst (Essential Unleashed Pet F1)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63258&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Rending Vines (Optional F2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63094&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Enveloping Haze (Optional F3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you skip the opener, you just have to use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger to unlock Unleashed Ambush to proceed with the quickness rotation.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;The 3 pet skills have no cast time but venomous outburst is your biggest contributor. The other 2 may be skipped to lower your APM if they slow your rotation. The damage difference is negligible.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you use a 2KRO&#x2F;3KRO keyboard, your simultaneous cast of pet skills may result in input failure. Most gaming keyboards are 6KRO, allowing all the buttons to be pressed at the same time. Alternatively, can just use F2.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;quickness-rotation&quot;&gt;Quickness Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build starts off with a very simple quickness rotation through the trait &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2268&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Power.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unleashed Ambush
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;69223&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Neurotoxin Burst OR&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63129&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Sundering Volley&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🔃 Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unleashed Ambush (other weapon)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue with DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;dps-rotation-l-to-r-a-d-r-to-l-d-t&quot;&gt;DPS Rotation - L to R (A&#x2F;D) R to L (D&#x2F;T)&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After using your 2nd Unleash Ambush -&amp;gt; use the skills from left to right for Axe&#x2F;Dagger and from right to left for Dagger&#x2F;Torch. The first skill you use will be recharged faster. This skill is bolded in the rotation and should be cast twice before &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63344&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Pet and reentering the opener. This will maximise the effect of &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;1064&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Quick Draw. This is bolded in the rotation below.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dagger&#x2F;Torch &lt;strong&gt;5&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;432 then 5
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill 5&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 4&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 3&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 2&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill 5&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pet F2 (if available)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue with Opener (see above)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Axe&#x2F;Dagger &lt;strong&gt;2&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;345 then 2
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill 2&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 3&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 4&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill 5&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill 2&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pet F2 (if available)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue with Opener (see above)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Your pet skills don&#x27;t interrupt your rotation and you may use them as desired.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Any condition based spider or devourer pet is preferred due to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;1099&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Arachnophobia&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger before your 🔃 &lt;strong&gt;Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; refreshes, your Unleashed Ambush will not be ready.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger too early will lead to a large DPS loss. Using it late will lead to a small DPS loss and maintain quickness.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crowd Control Skills&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;43068&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Tail Lash (F1)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exploding Spores (Utility Alternative)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12476&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spike Trap (Utility Alternative)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring other pets if you need more&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;benchmark&quot;&gt;Benchmark&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This bench was done with ascended food, standard utiltiies and without infusions.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
