&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQQgHx45SBd5AHkAARsAAKUBAACsAQAADxsAAEAQARMAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADMwBaAAUAAA==&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;6B9111F0B1CF94B4A4052FF39FB4E5041702FCDF&#x2F;52565.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Black Moa&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;peticon&quot; style=&quot;background: url(&#x27;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;render.guildwars2.com&#x2F;file&#x2F;58AFDFDFDDB8325F5E076C2400C63D450C15EA09&#x2F;2604592.png&#x27;) 50% 50% no-repeat;&quot;&gt;Juvenile Wallow&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;31914,63157,12633,12491,63163&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;32,30,72&#x27; data-armory-32-traits=&#x27;1606,970,1945&#x27; data-armory-30-traits=&#x27;1069,1700,1888&#x27; data-armory-72-traits=&#x27;2301,2263,2271&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63344&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Pet using Sword&#x2F;Axe&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;general-rotation&quot;&gt;General Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The entirety of quickness Untamed rotation can be summarised into two steps.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opener (optional)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickness Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;opener&quot;&gt;Opener&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The opener can give a very good burst, especially when the boss has different phases.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63344&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Pet&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12633&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Sic &#x27;Em!&quot;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 pet skills (can be cast simultaneously)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63209&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Venomous Outburst&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63258&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Rending Vines&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63094&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Enveloping Haze&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you skip the opener, you have to use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger to unlock Unleash Ambush to give quickness.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Starting the opener with sword will trigger &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;103574&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of the Claw right at the beginning which is a significant initial DPS burst.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you use a 2KRO&#x2F;3KRO keyboard, your simultaneous cast of pet skills may result in input failure. Most gaming keyboards are 6KRO, allowing all the buttons to be pressed at the same time. Alternatively, you press the three pet skills one by one as fast as you can.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;quickness-rotation&quot;&gt;Quickness Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build starts off with a very simple quickness rotation through the trait &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2268&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Power.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unleashed Ambush
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63438&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relentless Whirl OR&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63336&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Deft Strike&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🔃 Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unleashed Ambush (other weapon)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue with DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;dps-rotation-2-3-4-5-7-8&quot;&gt;DPS Rotation (2&#x2F;3&#x2F;4&#x2F;5&#x2F;7&#x2F;8)&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After using your 2nd Unleash Ambush -&amp;gt; Autos about to start&#x2F;started&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weapon 2
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63335&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Wild Swing OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;69203&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Pounce&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weapon 3
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63197&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Overbearing Smash OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12482&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Serpent&#x27;s Strike&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weapon 4
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63131&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Savage Shock Wave OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12638&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Path of Scars&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weapon 5
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63208&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleashed Thump OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12639&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Whirling Defense&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilities 7&#x2F;8 if available +&#x2F;- Pet skill (F3)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exploding Spores OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12633&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Sic &#x27;Em!&quot;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;64882&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Undead Plague&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optional Weapon 2 on refresh&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Autos (till 🔃 &lt;strong&gt;Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; refreshes)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63344&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Pet -&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue with Quickness Rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12633&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Sic &#x27;Em!&quot; on cooldown or during a comfortable window when you are not pressing any skills.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Your pet skills don&#x27;t interrupt your rotation and you may use them as desired. Any power based pet is viable.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Try not to cancel &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63438&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relentless Whirl or &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12639&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Whirling Defense.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;You may wish to introduce a slight delay after casting &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63438&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relentless Whirl&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;The sequence of button presses are similar on both weapons.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you are slow on your rotation, you can skip Weapon 3.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63147&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Unleash Ranger before your 🔃 &lt;strong&gt;Weapon Swap&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; refreshes, your Unleashed Ambush will not be ready.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Dragging your feet on using ambush will lead to a small 1-2k DPS loss. Swapping Unleash Mode too early will lead to a higher DPS loss.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;relic-of-the-claw-uptime&quot;&gt;Relic of the Claw Uptime&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;103574&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of the Claw is triggered by your CC skills. These are littered between your important skill casts except during the end of the hammer phase. If you have followed the DPS rotation above &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exploding Spores should be available towards the later part of your hammer DPS rotation.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you started off with the wrong weapon, then remember to reserve &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exploding Spores for hammer.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crowd Control Skills&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63336&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Deft Strike before &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63438&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relentless Whirl&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12638&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Path of Scars before &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;12639&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Whirling Defense&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;63157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exploding Spores during hammer rotation&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your pet F3 skills deal CC through the trait &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;1945&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Beastly Warden&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;benchmark&quot;&gt;Benchmark&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This bench was done with ascended food, standard utiltiies and without infusions.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
